e/93.0.4577.15 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "video_ext": "mp4", "audio_ext": "none", "abr": 0, "vbr": 1736.821, "format": "dash-2069587227218010v - 1080x1920 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by iamchrischung", "description": "Viral reel breakdown pt 3", "duration": 48.809, "timestamp": 1770427802, "uploader_id": "17814358", "uploader": "Chris Chung", "channel": "iamchrischung", "like_count": 56733, "comment_count": 958, "comments": [{"author": "ckdm_lifestyle", "author_id": "36995563009", "id": "18352036501234336", "text": "🔥", "timestamp": 1775177988}, {"author": "ninas.studygram", "author_id": "69691556004", "id": "18346519528212856", "text": "I also follow her. The first thing that hooked me was her beautiful/adorable face and smile (so I stopped to listen what she want’s to say), she has positive vibe, she feels excited about her topic, she is relatable - not like some distant high authority, but still seems credible and authentic. \n\nShe is able to explain her topic clearly and with good rhytm, so you don’t scroll past so quickly. She uses the same camera angles and posing over and over again (her videos feel as a serie). \n\nI think she is very good example of influencers popularizing science and also giving good role model for women 😊 . \n\nShe has very pleasant personality for doing science communication on this platform. Love her!", "timestamp": 1775113664}, {"author": "billionaireattitude01", "author_id": "50714085495", "id": "18128434153564903", "text": "@emonthebrain", "timestamp": 1774875192}, {"author": "cutie_catpie", "author_id": "61384765139", "id": "18159663115435222", "text": "If the content is about real education, I don’t care about how „you catch me“. It‘s called a hook anyway, and you learn these things in journalism (in some instances in academic writing, too). You can always laugh off a ludicrous hook later, and many people really need education– and those cultural hooks are the only way they get it.", "timestamp": 1774469453}, {"author": "funnyclips_hub_1", "author_id": "41117127572", "id": "18128944285486205", "text": "This guy knows it’s mainly because of her looks but he is doing it for comments to blow up his video, that is a real strategy", "timestamp": 1774280488}, {"author": "nickimarieinc", "author_id": "10612294", "id": "18004924889887782", "text": "I have no time for this… i believe in real chatter … less views is fine if im grabbing the right people who need me ❤️ \n\nThere is no one size fits all to this… ❤️ \n\nDon’t become a robot people- BE YOU 🤌", "timestamp": 1773842291}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/630092322_25702287199434361_1595193510328222190_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4LmRlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=101&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFlRxrSEnyhsl5_uM5zBR8PEt3_SGsLGwzrM2ET76oUuVqV6bJkqwkfYDOPRB3nrXY&_nc_ohc=rrmtmWlYjBkQ7kNvwG8MCnf&_nc_gid=ezrX0Tdepe51r9CHABTJiQ&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af3VlBNy7eZXDKekJjvAkP4Q-vSOHIuf7oKbAy5791R4MA&oe=69D7AA68&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 640, "height": 1136, "id": "0", "resolution": "640x1136"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/630092322_25702287199434361_1595193510328222190_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4LmRlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=101&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFlRxrSEnyhsl5_uM5zBR8PEt3_SGsLGwzrM2ET76oUuVqV6bJkqwkfYDOPRB3nrXY&_nc_ohc=rrmtmWlYjBkQ7kNvwG8MCnf&_nc_gid=ezrX0Tdepe51r9CHABTJiQ&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af3VlBNy7eZXDKekJjvAkP4Q-vSOHIuf7oKbAy5791R4MA&oe=69D7AA68&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 750, "height": 1331, "id": "1", "resolution": "750x1331"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yy